These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bongani, tiparillo, alhambra, dunhill, chaman, bolivar
1. the bongani-smoker is in the middle##1
2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Cigar   | bolivar | alhambra | dunhill | bongani | tiparillo | oliveros | chaman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: climbing, rugby, water-polo, skiing, parkour, handball, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Sport   | climbing | parkour | water-polo | handball | skiing | rugby | basketball |

