.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: chinese, russian, french, nigerian, british, australian, italian
1. the nigerian is on the right of the russian##1
2. the french is in the middle##1
3. the nigerian is on the far right##1
4. the italian is on the left of the russian##1
5. the chinese is on the right of the british##1
6. the australian is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | british | chinese | australian | french | italian | russian | nigerian |

