3. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the fan of country is on the far right##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of funk##1
6. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |    3    |     4     |       5       |   6   |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | hip-hop | blues | jazz | funk | electronic | country |

